package leecode;

import java.util.*;

class Solution_containDuplicate {
    public boolean containsDuplicate(int[] nums) {
        int size = nums.length;
        Map<Integer,String> checkMap = new HashMap<Integer,String>();
        for(int i = 0; i<size; i++){
            if(checkMap.get(nums[i])=="Stored"){
                return true;
            }
            else{
                checkMap.put(nums[i],"Stored");
            }
        }
        return false;
    }
}
